title: Avril Lavigne Sparks Ryan Cabrera Dating Rumors
text:
Comments The 'Girlfriend' hitmaker was spotted on a pumpkin shopping with the 33-year-old singer on Tuesday, October 20. 
Avril Lavigne has sparked dating rumors with Ryan Cabrera after they were spotted on a pumpkin shopping in Beverly Hills on Tuesday, October 20. After hitting up grocery store together, Avril's assistant reportedly drove her and Ryan back to her home. In some photos obtained by Mail Online , Avril suffered nip-slip while leaving the store with Ryan, who was carrying two pumpkins. The "Complicated" singer wore a black sheer skeleton mini dress and a low-cut black tank paired with black-and-white sneakers and black sunglasses. Ryan, meanwhile, wore a black hat, a white tee, black ripped pants and Mickey Mouse plimsolls. While both singers' representatives have not commented on the report yet, Avril and Ryan may not in a romantic relationship after all. Ryan is dating entertainment reporter Katie Krause. The pair were last seen together in a picture they posted on Instagram earlier this month. They visited Halloween Horror Nights at Universal Studios with friends. A photo posted by Ryan Cabrera (@ryancabrera) on Oct 2, 2015 at 8:21am PDT In an older picture, Ryan was being kissed on the cheek by Katie. The photo was seemingly taken at Katie's birthday party.
